MyAspNetApp (Solution)
|
+---> MyAspNetApp (ASP.NET Web and API)
|   |
|   +---> MyAspNetApp.Business
|   |
|   +---> MyAspNetApp.Data
|
+---> MyAspNetApp.Business (Service Layer)
|   |
|   +---> MyAspNetApp.Abstraction.Business
|   |
|   +---> MyAspNetApp.Abstraction.Data
|   |
|   +---> MyAspNetApp.Abstraction
|   |
|   +---> MyAspNetApp.Shared
|
+---> MyAspNetApp.Data (Repository Layer)
|   |
|   +---> MyAspNetApp.Abstraction.Data
|   |
|   +---> MyAspNetApp.Abstraction
|   |
|   +---> MyAspNetApp.Shared
|
+---> MyAspNetApp.Abstraction.Business (Service Interfaces)
|   |
|   +---> MyAspNetApp.Contracts
|
+---> MyAspNetApp.Abstraction.Data (Repository Interfaces)
|   |
|   +---> MyAspNetApp.Entity
|
+---> MyAspNetApp.Contracts (View Models and DTOs)
|
+---> MyAspNetApp.Entity (Entities and Custom Data Types)
|
+---> MyAspNetApp.Abstraction (OtherCommon Interfaces)
|
+---> MyAspNetApp.Shared (Common Helpers)